 Products 





















 
Certain Federal, State, Local, and Educational projects are funded by the
American Recovery and Reinvestment Act (ARRA).
Section 1605 of the ARRA states, 
“None of the funds appropriated or otherwise made available by this
Act may be used for a projects for the construction, alteration, maintenance,
or repair of a public building or public work
unless all the iron, steel, and manufactured goods used in the project are 
produced in the United States.”



    ARRA Certificate of Compliance 
    



 















